name: test-steps
type: list of maps or list of string
purpose: TODO
status: proposal

motivation:
  Store information about every single step under test-case.

stories:
  - As a tester I want to know what test doing step-by-step
    without looking to the code.

examples: |
  test-steps:
      - step: Send message with Client.A to Router.B
        expected: Message was sucessfully sended.
      - step: Receive message with Client.B from Router.A
        expected: Message was sucessfully received.

  test-steps:
      - First step (Try to support easyform test-steps without map/expected)
      - Second step
      - ...
